{"tid":1516664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」聽日林奠會現身中環食lunch!!!","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T16:10:01.000Z","uid":103102,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5343f2eb7bec41e66a73afd8614f166e0ab89cd9","tid":1516664,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xMJ5qhq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxMJ5qhq.jpg&h=6b8a0ca5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QYF3Wo7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQYF3Wo7.jpg&h=58691587&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫就寫11點開始 不過通常有遲冇早<br />\n特首話要建立溝通平台 有咩好過親身對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知道林太仲有好多支持者 聽日就有個好機會親身過去同佢打氣喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.s. 收到料話會有防暴扮服務生 自己小心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時間革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d915c24b83b74dcff4bf2ab5cd5d8f150dbc7eb1","tid":1516664,"uid":231818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"dc43b49043b03b0632b28616cb5e637917a6d99f","tid":1516664,"uid":103102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:46:29.000Z","msg":"仆街打錯字 黎多次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1883212c7bd8f6692511b731359771990fe51116","tid":1516664,"uid":103102,"li